name: Blender Studies 32.01
description:
Mexican amethyst & quartz (var.)

This work is a commentary on the extraction of natural resources through the examination of structure, color, and form found in a 3d matrix created in Blender. The final render was derived from an image of amethyst and quartz mined in Mexico.

A 1/1 donation match to an NFT purchase by @annaxmalina through “Bangon, a fundraiser event in cooperation with a\terHEN and Mono8 Gallery for the benefit of the victims of typhoon Odette in the Philippines.”
